{"tid":2320152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世界人權日，又到Twitter 時間啦","createTime":"2020-12-10T14:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T16:03:01.000Z","uid":306614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62343e079806299f8a85298def65471b26b5f3d9","tid":2320152,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"12月10日為「世界人權日」，今年「選入」聯合國人權組織的中國繼續打壓維吾爾族人和香港人的人權。「世界人權日」前夕，據報導多名中國維權律師被限制外出。<br />\n<br />\n各國議員及外媒一直對中國打壓人權的狀況多所譴責。「世界人權日」有關中國或香港推文摘錄如下（將陸續更新），請大家一齊努力推，提升國際關注，對中國和港共政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n議員政要<br />\n<br />\n🟢 Assita Kanko,  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Assita_Kanko/status/1337019888704040962?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAssita_Kanko%2Fstatus%2F1337019888704040962%3Fs%3D09&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2Wrppvqf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=f33e4dd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAssita_Kanko%2Fstatus%2F1337019888704040962%3Fs%3D09&h=8376b7af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Assita_Kanko/status/1337019888704040962?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n🟢 Antonio Tajani, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Antonio_Tajani/status/1337019033485512706?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntonio_Tajani%2Fstatus%2F1337019033485512706%3Fs%3D09&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2Wrppvqf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1ab427b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntonio_Tajani%2Fstatus%2F1337019033485512706%3Fs%3D09&h=cbc610f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Antonio_Tajani/status/1337019033485512706?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n🟢 Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bueti/status/1336705071401361416?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbueti%2Fstatus%2F1336705071401361416%3Fs%3D09&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2Wrppvqf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=d9fb6791\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com